    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds good in theory but i'm worried about my margins. if i have to pay everyone way more, i'll probably have to raise my prices or cut staff just to stay afloat. aren't there risks to that, like maybe causing more unemployment or making it harder for local shops to compete?",
